M|lean-startup|This skill is based on Eric Ries' Lean Startup methodology. For the complete framework, research, and case studies:
M|lean-startup|- [*"The Lean Startup"*](https://www.amazon.com/Lean-Startup-Entrepreneurs-Continuous-Innovation/dp/0307887898?tag=wondelai00-20) by Eric Ries
M|lean-startup|- [*"The Startup Way"*](https://www.amazon.com/Startup-Way-Companies-Entrepreneurial-Management/dp/1101903201?tag=wondelai00-20) by Eric Ries (applying Lean Startup to established companies)
M|lean-startup|**Eric Ries** is an entrepreneur and author best known for developing the Lean Startup methodology. He was co-founder and CTO of IMVU, where he pioneered continuous dpl and customer dev practices that